# Hack: Deploying with git

Add the following to your Rakefile

    task :deploy do
      ENV['PRODUCTION_HOST'] ||= "www.yourhost.com"
      system("ssh #{PRODUCTION_HOST} 'set -x; cd /path/to/app/install && git pull && bundle'")
    end

Then run

    $ bundle exec rake deploy

